          "common props (className, src, title, value, variant, …)",
          "Design components (Button, Badge, Avatar, Alert, Nav, CardFooter, Progress, …)",
          "utilities actually present in Design codegen today (flex, flex-col, space-y-*, p-*, gap-*, …)",
          "pilot glosses on IDE-ready packs"
